Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:03.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watching Fairy Tail keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:12.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Gray crying? {Two "Gray's" in a row}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:20.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray's teacher, Ul, turned her own body into the ice that sealed Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:25.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated his fellow student, Lyon, who was plotting on resurrecting the demon, but... {I know older is in the Japanese, but it makes the wording awkward in English}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora's been resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for even more who-knows-what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:41.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to mystery is right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:44.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world's a wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,which we're already wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:52.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement gets my heart racing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:59.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What is real, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see tomorrow, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:10.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The only part leveling up is my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:15.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just throw away our daily life together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:23.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! S. O. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:29.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Living itself will be our training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:32.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for even more who-knows-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:40.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be satisfied with just the normal answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical wonder life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:51.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best living our life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that voice just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait, was that even a voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was your stomach growling, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I know you're joking, it still ticks me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was this Deliora we're dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it's been resurrected!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That light! It's the Moon Drip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:45.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, you really should eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:51.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I feed you to a rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:56.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora may be able to roar, but the Moon Drip ceremony continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means its resurrection isn't yet complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Deliora's below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can break up the ceremony we can still halt the progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't got time to waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:20.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you off quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:28.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can manipulate this as well, my little Salamander...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It fixed itself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can control the time of objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:49.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I can return the crystal to a time before it was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time? I can't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Ark is a magic that has been erased from history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:04:00.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's one of the Lost Magics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:05.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, shall I progress the crystal's time into the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:26.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can also stop its time, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like it won't work on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:34.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't you have the sharp eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:37.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is accurate to say that it will not work on living creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:43.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly why I cannot simply reverse time on the ice that is Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:47.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to resurrect this thing only to let Lyon defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon might be happy with that, but what's in it for his friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:03.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I only joined them all quite recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you really after?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my... I can't slip anything by you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:20.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reitei-sama... Or rather that spoiled brat could never defeat Deliora in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's really dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd defeat it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:26.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make it mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There exist techniques to control even immortal beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:42.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be incredible for me to control such awesome power, do you not think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid. Sorry I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:53.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted it to be a plan that's gonna get me really fired up to stop! {I don't think this is the correct interpretation (see the manga for mine), but it's worded so vaguely that I can't say for sure that it isn't. I reworded it slightly to fit the above line (which I am sure of}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:01.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There will always come a time when one needs power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And when that time comes, I'll believe in my own power, and the power of my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ego will lead to your destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ceiling, speed your time and crumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each and every one of you are screwin' up this island for your own stupid reasons! {nice wording}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not gonna take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:31.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can those wild flames capture my Time Ark?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Ark, Time Pork, whatever! {in the manga, I did "pork" too}{maybe change to "Park" because it's a closer pun in English, but it loses the food reference which is more Natsu-like...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell off this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I can manipulate time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One second from now I'm gonna blow you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now the Moon Drip will stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:08.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he was doing it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too late! The ceremony's already over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:31.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... Something truly fearsome has begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, let's escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No matter what happens, I will not leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:07:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's destroy that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will... defeat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:17.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:22.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to surpass Ul, I will be the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks way more impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:34.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, we meet again... Deliora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Around here that'd be Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:46.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some years ago she secluded herself in the mountains in shock after she lost her daughter. {What happened to Ultear isn't clear yet. But "lost" is such a good vague word. It implie death, but it can mean so many other things.}{I read that Zalty is actually Ul's daughter? So should this be "lost" or "taken away"? Did Ul think she's dead?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, no wizard's come close to Ul around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:55.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul, huh? I wonder if she'll take me on as an apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:09:00.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one monster that Ul was not able to defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:04.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will... defeat it... with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:08.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just picked up that brat, and now he's your apprentice? How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to learn magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it such a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:16.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I enough as a replacement for your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:27.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon. I have never thought of you as a replacement for my daughter, not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are you. My beloved apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:38.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... going to... surpass you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me. {The rest? What did Lyon do? Except cause this whole mess...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will seal Deliora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how long it took to melt that ice? {Yes, you told him in the last episode... remember?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:10.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just repeating history!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I'll melt it and challenge it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:19.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, this is the one thing that can stop it! {varying the language to make it look less like the line before it}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:38.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped you before 'cause I didn't want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I didn't get through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:48.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna use that magic, then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so loud! My eardrums are gonna burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna give up 'till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora was already dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:33.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For 10 years, its life force has been sapped by Ul's ice... {"sapped trapped" doesn't work very well}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All we saw was its last moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:50.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't compare... I can never surpass Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your teacher is pretty amazing. {using present tense to imply Natsu believes like gray that Ul is still "alive"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:02.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will seal your darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:11.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much... Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul's ice was melted into water and flowed into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Ul is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Gray said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul will watch over her two students from the ocean, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's telling them, "don't fight any longer."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:03.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I wasn't sure what was gonna happen there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ul's really quite amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:09.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we all managed to finish an S class quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we can go up to the second floor now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! We're gonna be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, you have something to do, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:31.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the real point of this job to save the villagers who have been turned into demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:35.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The S class quest is not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:40.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Deliora's dead, so won't this stop the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:44.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The source of that curse was not Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:49.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The tremendous magical power of the Moon Drip has caused disaster to befall the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Deliora has now crumbled would not have improved the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll hurry up and cure 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you: I have no idea. {I'm sort of making a joke out of the "itteoku" here, in case the line seems a bit silly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"What!" {perhaps I added this joke, perhaps I didn't?  No one will ever know!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if you guys don't know, how else are we going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago when we came here, we knew there was a village on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we did not interfere with the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And they never came to see us even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years... Not once?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:39.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, the Moon Drip would have landed on the ruins every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:43.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's really strange that they'd never come to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there remain a number of questions about the effect the Moon Drip has on people's bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:53.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Are you trying to say that it's not your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it. We've been under the same light for 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:05.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. They're hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:09.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway this is a job for you guild people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't {\i1}think{\i0} so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who destroyed the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. {better way of putting this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry, and all the others are people who had their families taken from them by Deliora. {what about Yuka? I think the writers totally forgot about him}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:26.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why we all cooperated with Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought that if it's Lyon, he'd be able to defeat Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:33.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He would finally be able to get revenge for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They have their own version of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:39.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to criticize what they did in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go? But how are we going to lift the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go join a guild somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:17:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll gain friends and rivals, and I know you'll find a new reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pointless... Just go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's deserted. {"here" was on both lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the village is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why did everyone vanish? {"gone" was on both lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:24.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm gonna get some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:28.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all returned? There's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, hurry to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the village was all messed up yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back the way it was. How the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost as if time has been reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:52.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all fixed up now, so it'd be better for you not to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it him?  Couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he had a change of heart? {too many "wait"s}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:15.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, our bags! {How about getting a replacement shirt?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:24.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see Bobo's grave is back to normal too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you all who returned the village to normal, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:36.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Wizards! How long exactly until you destroy the moon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying the moon will be a simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did she just say that with a straight face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye... Well, that's Erza for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:19:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I have something I want to clarify first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you gather everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us review.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:15.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all appeared in these forms after the moon turned purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precice, it's only when that moon comes out do we look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And considering what we've heard, this has been happening for the past 3 years, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It has probably been that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:35.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However the Moon Drip has occurred on this island every night for those past three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have been able to see the light falling on the ruins every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:41.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The pitfall was also resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:48.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She just said "Kya!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not my fault! This is not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:59.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, was it not the most suspicious place on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's acting like nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's tough... {takamashii can mean physically tough}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why you never investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is tradition in this village never to go near those ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:19.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is no time to be bound by traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had victims, and just look at the amount of the reward for the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:30.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please tell us the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We don't really understand ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:39.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In truth we've tried to investigate those ruins many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:43.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We never use weapons, but we took them up, I trimmed my sideburns perfectly, {Actually the punctuation for full sentences connected is semi-colons, but they look so "stuffy" in subtitles}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and we all headed toward those ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we couldn't get near.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:53.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As we walked toward the ruins, before we knew it we were back at the village gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:57.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot come close to those ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean? You can't get near them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all went inside them, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:08.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't tell you because we thought you wouldn't believe us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth. Now matter how many times we tried to go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...not a single villager has ever set foot in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so. {too many "as"s}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:26.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Titania.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already figured out the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:49.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to destroy the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:02.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:05.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:15.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing after your profile left only in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:27.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "I never want to see your face again," when you left me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:32.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tears on your cheek said it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you felt like you'd be swallowed up in the waves of contradiction
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:45.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you always held back your tears, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:56.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a strong person," they said, but everyone overestimated you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:23:05.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and before you knew it you lost sight of who you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:09.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the sun I thought would always be near me collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the light shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:16.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbing out the truths and the lies of one day, altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:29.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,still, ironically, chasing after your profile in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Happy's Fairy Tail Lectures!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:37.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we're going to tell you the secrets behind Celestial Spirit Wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:43.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Spirits can be called by the wizard as many times as their mutual trust permits. {"often" implies "time" as in days of the week, but that isn't dependant on trust but rather on the contract}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:47.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And they say the stronger the wizard's magical power, the stronger the Celestial Spirits become!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:51.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to new Celestial Spirits showing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:54.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand, Bow, Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.19,0:24:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, did you know that there're cats in the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if you're talking about the moon, you mean rabbits, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:07.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... There's no way that rabbits would be so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:09.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no grass or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:12.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there are any fish on the moon either, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Reach it! To that Sky! {I didn't come up with anything better for the manga chapter.}{I don't like this lit. translation much... suggestions?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do the moon cats eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sayin' there ain't no cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:24.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww... I wanted to try eating a moon fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.16,0:24:26.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
